      <h1>Masters</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        Are you looking for a master&#039;s degree at a world-class university where high-quality education, the best lecturers and leading researchers are all part of the package? Leiden University offers almost 80 English taught master&#039;s programmes: you’re certain to find one that suits you.</p>
      </article>
